{"tid":1693144,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【和理非升級】響office、department、職場搵你嘅同路人！","createTime":"2019-11-04T12:22:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T14:27:15.000Z","uid":59815,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"29d55e458ff93fb963d41408dabf0cba1fd52782","tid":1693144,"uid":59815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T12:22:28.000Z","msg":"點解九月罷工搞唔成？唔係因為文宣唔夠，係因為八五罷工之後，中共出招，職場篤灰之風蔓延，航空界唔敢再罷。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁可以點做？文宣解決唔到嘅問題，要由真人響office度解決！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ej7C2jE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fej7C2jE.jpg&h=8241dc37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><strong>【五個步驟&mdash;&mdash;組織職場手足】</strong></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n運動發展到今日，大家都明白我哋係要打持久戰，同呢個腐敗嘅政權鬥長命，所以我哋更加要擴大自己嘅力量，團結我哋嘅自己人﹗嚟緊呢個星期會同大家分享吓，點樣組織自己友嘅具體方法，希望大家都可以係自己職場運用啦﹗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1) <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">辨認手足</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 戴口罩返工、有香港鎖匙扣、有和你返工同快閃嘅活動日子都遲返、留意公司或者同事群組有冇嘢講抗爭議題<br />\n<br />\n2)<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 開群組</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：交流資訊如果有興趣嘅人都可以加入(不過要提防管理層同二五仔)<br />\n<br />\n3) <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">從簡單行動開始</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：戴口罩、貼貼紙memo、Airdrop文宣等<br />\n<br />\n4) <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">進一步組織</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：組團快閃、約埋去集會、一齊諗點支援運動，另外亦要了解各人就罷工等不同升級行動嘅看法<br />\n<br />\n5) <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">組織工會</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：令自己更有牙力，除咗政治表態，亦關注行業權益，增加職場話語權！"},{"pid":"c187df7f06a148bda5d4e914d42cde4f1cee8fb0","tid":1693144,"uid":89006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T12:34:45.000Z","msg":"🔴二百萬三罷聯合陣線🔴<br />\n立即加入二百萬三罷聯合陣線，以行業為基礎，以工會為組織，注入抗爭的新動力，並以二百萬人的大罷工為最終目標<br />\n<br />\n二百萬三罷聯合陣線頻道<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkonstrike\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVcfG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=f9cac25e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkonstrike</a><br />\n<br />\n二百萬三罷聯合陣線（公海）<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/FhM2GRbY1ThsEzrnbEyduA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FFhM2GRbY1ThsEzrnbEyduA&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVcfG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=af923fb3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/FhM2GRbY1ThsEzrnbEyduA</a>"},{"pid":"e24995955e5e86ee5ccfaadc3c435a963d2551e1","tid":1693144,"uid":89006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T12:36:28.000Z","msg":"10點鐘新口號！&rdquo;組織工會，全面罷工！&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1693050/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1693050/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"2c3db8e06b54acfb29479b868d70fb2b56c2488d","tid":1693144,"uid":182185,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"29d55e458ff93fb963d41408dabf0cba1fd52782","tid":1693144,"uid":59815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T12:22:28.000Z","msg":"點解九月罷工搞唔成？唔係因為文宣唔夠，係因為八五罷工之後，中共出招，職場篤灰之風蔓延，航空界唔敢再罷。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁可以點做？文宣解決唔到嘅問題，要由真人響office度解決！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ej7C2jE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u